/**
 * forcefully equips an item to a slot
 * kicks out conflicting items if possible
 *
 * This CAN fail, so listen to return value
 * Why? YOU MIGHT EQUIP TO A MOB WITHOUT A CERTAIN SLOT!
 *
 * @params
